title: Eddie Can’t Believe What His Son Purchased for $75 Bucks! + Lunchbox Calls Santa To Complain + Raymundo Claims He Saw Female Country Artist in a JACKED UP Truck…We Investigate!
itunes:title: Eddie Can’t Believe What His Son Purchased for $75 Bucks! + Lunchbox Calls Santa To Complain + Raymundo Claims He Saw Female Country Artist in a JACKED UP Truck…We Investigate!
description:
Eddie says he can’t believe what his oldest son bought with the money he earned blowing leaves at Bobby’s house. Lunchbox calls Santa to complain for gifts he never got as a kid. Raymundo says he saw a female country artist driving around listening to their own music. We give her a call to see if it’s true.
